SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a

    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"

LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"
ORDER BY a."AccessId", m."ModuleId", t."ModuleId"

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"
ORDER BY a."AccessId", m."ModuleId", t."ModuleId"

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"
ORDER BY a."AccessId", m."ModuleId", t."ModuleId"

SELECT l."LicenseId", l."StartDate", l."LicenseStatus", l."EndDate", u."Username", a."AccessName", u."UserId", a."AccessId", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", (
    SELECT p."ProductName"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
    WHERE a."AccessId" = m0."AccessId"
    LIMIT 1)
FROM "Licenses" AS l
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON l."UserId" = u."UserId"
INNER JOIN "Accesss" AS a ON l."AccessId" = a."AccessId"

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"

SELECT l."LicenseId", l."StartDate", l."LicenseStatus", l."EndDate", u."Username", a."AccessName", u."UserId", a."AccessId", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", (
    SELECT p."ProductName"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
    WHERE a."AccessId" = m0."AccessId"
    LIMIT 1)
FROM "Licenses" AS l

2023-06-09 11:52:58.161 +01:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (6ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT l."LicenseId", l."StartDate", l."LicenseStatus", l."EndDate", u."Username", a."AccessName", u."UserId", a."AccessId", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", (
    SELECT p."ProductName"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
    WHERE a."AccessId" = m0."AccessId"
    LIMIT 1)
FROM "Licenses" AS l
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON l."UserId" = u."UserId"
INNER JOIN "Accesss" AS a ON l."AccessId" = a."AccessId"

FROM "Accesss" AS a

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"
ORDER BY a."AccessId", m."ModuleId", t."ModuleId"

    SELECT m."ModuleId", m."AccessId", m."CodMod", m."CodModPack", m."CreatedBy", m."CreatedDate", m."Description", m."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModulePackage", m."ModuleStatus", m."ProductId", p."ProductId" AS "ProductId0", p."CodProd", p."CreatedBy" AS "CreatedBy0", p."CreatedDate" AS "CreatedDate0", p."Description" AS "Description0", p."FileName", p."ImageId", p."LastModificatedDate" AS "LastModificatedDate0", p."LogoFilePath", p."ProductName", p."ProductStatus", p."ProductVersion", p."PublishDate"
    FROM "Modules" AS m
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"
ORDER BY a."AccessId", m."ModuleId", t."ModuleId"

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"

FROM "Accesss" AS a

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"

2023-06-09 13:13:36.535 +01:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (11ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"
ORDER BY a."AccessId", m."ModuleId", t."ModuleId"

SELECT l."LicenseId", l."StartDate", l."LicenseStatus", l."EndDate", u."Username", a."AccessName", u."UserId", a."AccessId", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", (
    SELECT p."ProductName"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
    WHERE a."AccessId" = m0."AccessId"
    LIMIT 1)
FROM "Licenses" AS l
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON l."UserId" = u."UserId"
INNER JOIN "Accesss" AS a ON l."AccessId" = a."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
ORDER BY l."LicenseId", u."UserId", a."AccessId"

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a

) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"

    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"

2023-06-09 16:04:33.458 +01:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"
ORDER BY a."AccessId", m."ModuleId", t."ModuleId"

SELECT a."AccessId", a."AccessName", a."LastModificatedDate", m."ModuleName", m."ModuleId", t."ProductName", t."ModuleId", t."ProductId"
FROM "Accesss" AS a
LEFT JOIN "Modules" AS m ON a."AccessId" = m."AccessId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p."ProductName", m0."ModuleId", p."ProductId", m0."AccessId"
    FROM "Modules" AS m0
    LEFT JOIN "Products" AS p ON m0."ProductId" = p."ProductId"
) AS t ON a."AccessId" = t."AccessId"
ORDER BY a."AccessId", m."ModuleId", t."ModuleId"

FROM "Accesss" AS a
